Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,‫=======================משפחה=======================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:51.02,Family Main,,0,0,0,,♪ We're more than just companions ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.02,0:22:53.18,Family Main,,0,0,0,,♪ Beyond what you would call friends ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:22:57.56,Family Secondary,,0,0,0,,♪ While we're all on the sea ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:56.48,Family Main,,0,0,0,,♪ We're each others own FAMILY! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.48,0:22:58.69,Family Main,,0,0,0,,♪ Not one of us are siblings ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:01.19,Family Main,,0,0,0,,♪ We don't share any blood ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.57,0:23:05.91,Family Main,,0,0,0,,♪ But our crew is still FAMILY! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.29,0:23:14.66,Family Main,,0,0,0,,♪ Survey maps galore, ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.66,0:23:19.21,Family Main,,0,0,0,,{\q2}♪ The biggest maps you've ever laid your eyes on ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.21,0:23:21.92,Family Main,,0,0,0,,♪ It wouldn't matter anyway, ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.92,0:23:24.67,Family Main,,0,0,0,,♪ You'll never find family like this ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.67,0:23:29.47,Family Main,,0,0,0,,♪ Only outstanding slackers and misfits ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.47,0:23:33.10,Family Main,,0,0,0,,♪ Can come aboard our MOTHER SHIP ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.10,0:23:37.02,Family Main,,0,0,0,,♪ Forsake all reason, then maybe ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.02,0:23:41.15,Family Main,,0,0,0,,♪ You can sail along with us ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:46.53,Family Main,,0,0,0,,♪ EVERYDAY ride out the storm ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.53,0:23:50.28,Family Main,,0,0,0,,♪ That's all we can ask for ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.28,0:23:54.12,Family Main,,0,0,0,,{\q2}♪ We'll find the greatest treasure, it's our quest, ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.12,0:24:00.29,Family Main,,0,0,0,,♪ with the aid of our MOTHER SHIP ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.42,0:24:05.22,Family Main,,0,0,0,,♪ The best people share a quirk, yeah ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.22,0:24:11.47,Family Main,,0,0,0,,♪ They can laugh like no one else can! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.43,0:24:14.56,Family Main,,0,0,0,,♪ We're more than just companions ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.56,0:24:16.64,Family Main,,0,0,0,,♪ Beyond what you would call friends ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.90,0:24:21.86,Family Secondary,,0,0,0,,♪ While there's fun and we're free! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.64,0:24:20.06,Family Main,,0,0,0,,♪ We're each other's own FAMILY! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.06,0:24:22.02,Family Main,,0,0,0,,♪ Not one of us are siblings, ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.02,0:24:25.03,Family Main,,0,0,0,,♪ We don't share any blood ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.03,0:24:29.32,Family Main,,0,0,0,,♪ But our crew is still FAMILY! ♪
